CHANGES IN VERSION 1.11.2 (2025-05-09)
--------------------------------------

SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES

    o Remove `get_slot_contents` function. Use `slot` function instead.
    
    o Change default aligner to HISAT2 from Bowtie2.
    
    o Change repository.
    
    o Update documentation.
    


CHANGES IN VERSION 1.5.2 (2024-04-23)
--------------------------------------

SIGNIFICANT USER-VISIBLE CHANGES

    o Slot name `reversed` of `CircSeqAlignTkCoverage` class was changed to `reverse`.

NEW FEATURES

    o Add GUI mode. See build_app() for details.



